description: Fast-Match behavior (small batch)
globs: ["apps/mobile/**", "server/**"]
---
- Invite max **1–3** providers ranked by ETA + rating + distance.
- Response TTL **60–90s**; expire deterministically server-side.
- If exactly one response → **auto-assign**.
- If multiple → show **≤2 cards** (ETA/rating/price). Expire the rest.
- Reveal exact address **after** match.
- If customer idle ≥60s on choose screen → auto‑assign best.